<p><a name="Keep"></a><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="4"><b>Keep up the good work</b></font><p>

<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3">KUDOS FOR embracing socialism in a nation that seems dead-set against it. I actually found your publication as I was doing research for an article on wealth distribution and the problems of the free-market capitalist system.<br>
Keep up your great and important work. <p>
There was a time when socialism was a real force in the United States--we can bring back many of those ideals, but it will take a long and organized struggle.<br>
<b>Katherine Brengle,</b> Bristol County, Mass.<p>

<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><a href="#Top">Back to the top</a></font><br>
